InputStream digunakake kanggo maca, OutputStream kanggo nulis. Loro-lorone disambungake minangka dekorator supaya sampeyan bisa maca/nulis kabeh jinis data saka kabeh jinis sumber.
Contone, sampeyan bisa nulis data primitif menyang file:
```File file = new File("C:/text.bin");
file.createNewFile();
DataOutputStream stream = new DataOutputStream(new FileOutputStream(file));
stream.writeBoolean(true);
stream.writeInt(1234);
stream.close();
```
Kanggo maca isine sing ditulis:
```File file = new File("C:/text.bin");
DataInputStream stream = new DataInputStream(new FileInputStream(file));
boolean isTrue = stream.readBoolean();
int value = stream.readInt();
stream.close();
System.out.printlin(isTrue + " " + value);
```
Sampeyan bisa nggunakake jinis stream liya kanggo nambah maca/nulis. Contone, sampeyan bisa ngenalake buffer kanggo efisiensi:
```DataInputStream stream = new DataInputStream(
    new BufferedInputStream(new FileInputStream(file)));
```
Sampeyan bisa nulis data liyane kayata obyek:
```MyClass myObject = new MyClass(); // MyClass kudu ngimplementasikake Serializable
ObjectOutputStream stream = new ObjectOutputStream(
    new FileOutputStream("C:/text.obj"));
stream.writeObject(myObject);
stream.close();
```
Sampeyan bisa maca saka sumber input sing beda:
```byte[] test = new byte[] {0, 0, 1, 0, 0, 0, 1, 1, 8, 9};
DataInputStream stream = new DataInputStream(new ByteArrayInputStream(test));
int value0 = stream.readInt();
int value1 = stream.readInt();
byte value2 = stream.readByte();
byte value3 = stream.readByte();
stream.close();
System.out.println(value0 + " " + value1 + " " + value2 + " " + value3);
```
Kanggo umume input stream, ana uga output stream. Sampeyan bisa nemtokake stream dhewe kanggo maca/nulis barang-barang khusus lan ana stream kompleks kanggo maca barang-barang kompleks (contone, ana Streams kanggo maca/nulis format ZIP).

