output:
Gunakake `StringWriter` tinimbang `StreamWriter`:

```
public static string SerializeObject<T>(this T toSerialize)
{
    XmlSerializer xmlSerializer = new XmlSerializer(toSerialize.GetType());

    using(StringWriter textWriter = new StringWriter())
    {
        xmlSerializer.Serialize(textWriter, toSerialize);
        return textWriter.ToString();
    }
}
```

Cathetan, penting nggunakake `toSerialize.GetType()` tinimbang `typeof(T)` ing konstruktor XmlSerializer: yen sampeyan nggunakake sing kapisan, kode kasebut nyakup kabeh subkelas `T` sing bisa ditindakake (sing cocog kanggo metode kasebut), nalika nggunakake sing keri dhewe bakal gagal nalika ngliwati jinis sing asale saka `T`. Ana sawetara conto kode ing Ideone sing nyengkuyung pratelan iki, kanthi XmlSerializer nguncalke `Exception` nalika `typeof(T)` digunakake, amarga sampeyan ngliwati instansi saka jinis turunan menyang metode sing nelpon SerializeObject sing ditetepake ing kelas dasar jinis turunan kasebut.

Uga, Ideone nggunakake Mono kanggo nglakokake kode; `Exception` sing bakal sampeyan entuk nggunakake runtime Microsoft .NET duwe `Message` sing beda karo sing ditampilake ing Ideone, nanging gagal kaya biasane.

