## Solusi Java 8
Kita bisa migunakake ```lambda expression``` utawa ```method reference``` sing dikenalaké ing Java 8. Yen kita duwé sawetara nilai String sing disimpen ing Priority Queue (nduwéni kapasitas 5) kita bisa nyedhiyani inline comparator (adhedhasar dawa String):
Migunakaké lambda expression
```PriorityQueue pq=
                    new PriorityQueue(5,(a,b) -> a.length() - b.length());
```
Migunakaké Method reference
```PriorityQueue pq=
                new PriorityQueue(5, Comparator.comparing(String::length));
```
Banjur kita bisa migunakaké salah sijiné kaya mangkéné:
```public static void main(String[] args) {
        PriorityQueue pq=
                new PriorityQueue(5, (a,b) -> a.length() - b.length());
       // utawa pq = new PriorityQueue(5, Comparator.comparing(String::length));
        pq.add("Apple");
        pq.add("PineApple");
        pq.add("Custard Apple");
        while (pq.size() != 0)
        {
            System.out.println(pq.remove());
        }
    }
```
Iki bakal nyithak:
```Apple
PineApple
Custard Apple
```
Kanggo mbalikke urutan (kanggo ngganti dadi antrian prioritas maksimum) cukup ganti urutan ing inline comparator utawa migunakaké ```reversed``` kaya mangkéné:
```PriorityQueue pq = new PriorityQueue(5,
                             Comparator.comparing(String::length).reversed());
```
Kita uga bisa migunakaké ```Collections.reverseOrder```:
```PriorityQueue pqInt = new PriorityQueue(10, Collections.reverseOrder());
PriorityQueue pq = new PriorityQueue(5,
                Collections.reverseOrder(Comparator.comparing(String::length))
```
Dadi kita bisa ndeleng yèn ```Collections.reverseOrder``` dioverload kanggo njupuk comparator sing bisa migunani kanggo obyek khusus. ```reversed``` sakbeneré migunakaké ```Collections.reverseOrder```:
```default Comparator reversed() {
    return Collections.reverseOrder(this);
}
```
offer() vs add()
Miturut documentasi

  > Metode offer nglebokaké unsur yen bisa, yèn ora ngasilaké false. Iki béda karo metode Collection.add, sing bisa gagal nambah unsur mung kanthi nguncalké pengecualian sing ora dicenthang. Metode offer dirancang kanggo digunakaké nalika gagal minangka kedadéan normal, dudu pengecualian, contoné, ing antrian kapasitas tetep (utawa "terbatas").

Nalika migunakaké antrian kanthi kapasitas winates, offer() umumé luwih disenengi tinimbang add(), sing bisa gagal nglebokaké unsur mung kanthi nguncalké pengecualian. Lan PriorityQueue minangka antrian prioritas tanpa wates adhedhasar tumpukan prioritas.

