Nalika obyek sing dilewati menyang ```await``` dudu Janji, ```await``` mung ngasilake nilai kasebut kaya kaanan langsung tinimbang nyoba ngrampungake. Dadi amarga sampeyan ngliwati ```await``` array (obyek Janji) ing kene tinimbang Janji, nilai sing diasilake saka await yaiku mung array kasebut, sing jinis ```Promise[]```.
