Pitakonan iki cukup jembar, iki ana rong solusi.

### Solusi 1: Cara Pambantu
Iki conto panggunaan Cara Pambantu sing bisa diowahi supaya cocog karo kabutuhan sampeyan:
```class SerializationHelper {
    static toInstance(obj: T, json: string) : T {
        var jsonObj = JSON.parse(json);
        if (typeof obj["fromJSON"] === "function") {
            obj["fromJSON"](jsonObj);
        }
        else {
            for (var propName in jsonObj) {
                obj[propName] = jsonObj[propName]
            }
        }
        return obj;
    }
}
```
Banjur gunakake:
```var json = '{"name": "John Doe"}',
    foo = SerializationHelper.toInstance(new Foo(), json);
foo.GetName() === "John Doe";
```

* Deserialisasi Lanjut
Iki uga bisa ngidini sawetara deserialisasi khusus kanthi nambahake metode ```fromJSON``` dhewe menyang kelas (iki cocog karo cara ```JSON.stringify``` wis nggunakake metode ```toJSON```, kaya sing ditampilake ing ngisor iki):
```interface IFooSerialized {
    nameSomethingElse: string;
}
class Foo {
  name: string;
  GetName(): string { return this.name }
  toJSON(): IFooSerialized {
      return {
          nameSomethingElse: this.name
      };
  }
  fromJSON(obj: IFooSerialized) {
        this.name = obj.nameSomethingElse;
  }
}
```
Banjur gunakake:
```var foo1 = new Foo();
foo1.name = "John Doe";
var json = JSON.stringify(foo1);
json === '{"nameSomethingElse":"John Doe"}';
var foo2 = SerializationHelper.toInstance(new Foo(), json);
foo2.GetName() === "John Doe";
```

### Solusi 2: Kelas Dasar
Cara liya sing bisa ditindakake yaiku kanthi nggawe kelas dhasar dhewe:
```class Serializable {
    fillFromJSON(json: string) {
        var jsonObj = JSON.parse(json);
        for (var propName in jsonObj) {
            this[propName] = jsonObj[propName]
        }
    }
}
class Foo extends Serializable {
    name: string;
    GetName(): string { return this.name }
}
```
Banjur gunakake:
```var foo = new Foo();
foo.fillFromJSON(json);
```

Ana akeh cara sing beda kanggo ngleksanakake deserialisasi khusus nggunakake kelas dhasar, lan pungkasane gumantung karo pilihan sampeyan dhewe.

Cara sing bener kanggo ngindhari serangan injeksi SQL, ora preduli database sing sampeyan gunakake, yaiku misahake data saka SQL, supaya data tetep data lan ora bakal diinterpretasekake minangka perintah dening parser SQL. Bisa nggawe pernyataan SQL kanthi bagean data sing diformat kanthi bener, nanging yen sampeyan ora ngerti kanthi lengkap rincian, sampeyan kudu tansah nggunakake prepared statements lan parameterized queries. Iki minangka pernyataan SQL sing dikirim lan diurai dening server database kanthi kapisah saka parameter apa wae. Kanthi cara iki, ora mungkin kanggo penyerang nyuntikake SQL sing jahat.

Sampeyan sejatine duwe rong opsi kanggo nggayuh iki:

1. Nggunakake PDO (kanggo driver database sing didhukung):
```
$stmt = $pdo->prepare('SELECT * FROM employees WHERE name = :name');
$stmt->execute([ 'name' => $name ]);

foreach ($stmt as $row) {
    // Nindakake sawetara perkara karo $row
}
```

2. Nggunakake MySQLi (kanggo MySQL):
Wiwit PHP 8.2+ kita bisa nggunakake execute_query() sing nyiapake, nggandhengake parameter, lan nglakokake pernyataan SQL ing siji cara:
```
$result = $dbConnection->execute_query('SELECT * FROM employees WHERE name = ?', [$name]);

while ($row = $result->fetch_assoc()) {
    // Nindakake sawetara perkara karo $row
}
```

Nganti PHP8.1:
```
$stmt = $dbConnection->prepare('SELECT * FROM employees WHERE name = ?');
$stmt->bind_param('s', $name); // 's' nemtokake jinis variabel => 'string'
$stmt->execute();

$result = $stmt->get_result();
while ($row = $result->fetch_assoc()) {
    // Nindakake sawetara perkara karo $row
}
```
Yen sampeyan nyambung menyang database liyane kajaba MySQL, ana opsi kapindho khusus driver sing bisa sampeyan rujuk (contone, pg_prepare() lan pg_execute() kanggo PostgreSQL). PDO minangka opsi universal.

